Package org.mozilla.pluglet.mozilla

Interface Summary
ByteRanges This interface is for setting up a range of bytes.
PlugletManager The PlugletManager interface includes functionality to get and post URLs, and return the user agent for the browser and a PlugletManager variable.
PlugletManager2 This interface extends the functionality of the PlugletManager interface, indicating functions to begin and end a wait cursor, etc.
PlugletPeer The PlugletPeer interface is the set of functions implemented by the browser to support a Pluglet instance.
PlugletStreamInfo This interface returns various information about the stream such as the MIME type and whether the stream is seekable.
PlugletTagInfo This interface provides information about the HTML tag on the page.
PlugletTagInfo2 This interface represents an extension to PlugletTagInfo.
